intent.user_query: What are the top 5 most frequently reported product issues (IssueDescription) based on data in the ServiceTickets table?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT IssueDescription, COUNT(*) AS IssueCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets GROUP BY IssueDescription ORDER BY IssueCount DESC LIMIT 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT IssueDescription, COUNT(*) AS IssueCount FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets GROUP BY IssueDescription ORDER BY IssueCount DESC LIMIT 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
